</p>
      <p>evaluated at the fit of the previous iteration <inline-formula id="IEq5"><alternatives><tex-math id="M19">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
